<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#006d98">أَيَقُولُ:</span> هَذَا النُّورُ يَاتِي مِنْ ضِيَاءِ أَمِيرَتِي<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">أَيَقُولُ:</span> هَذَا الْبَدْرُ يَسْعَدُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>إِذْ يَرَى فِي كُلِّ حِينٍ نُورَ رُوحِي وَزَوْجَتِي<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>لَكِنْ تُرَانِي مَا سَأَفْعَلُ حِينَهَا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فِي الأَرْضِ جِسْمِي دُونَ رُوحِي<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فِي الأَرْضِ أَشْقَى نَاظِرًا سَعْدَ الْقَمَرْ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فِي الأَرْضِ أَقْرِضُ سَامِعًا طَرَبَ الْقَمَرْ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>أَيَجِيءُ يَوْمٌ قَدْ أَغَارُ مِنَ الْقَمَرْ؟!<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>* * *<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>